quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,78,NguYe Onidalele ukuva nokubona neentliziyo (zokuqiqa); kuncinane eninombulelo ngako
  23,79,NguYe Onandisileyoemhlabeniwonkeyayeniyakuqokelelwa phambi kwaKhe nonke
  23,80,"Kananjalo nguYe Onika ubomi Enze ukufa, ikwanguYe Ojika ubusuku bube yimini. Ingaba aniyi kuqonda ke"
  23,81,"Nakanye, bona batsho izinto ezifana nezo zazisitshiwo ngabamandulo"
  23,82,"Bona bathi: “Ingaba xa sele sifile, sele singumhlaba namathambo, siza kuphinda sivuswe ngenyaniso"
  23,83,Sakuthenjiswa oko thina noobawo mkhulu bethu ngaphambili; oku akuyonto ngaphandle kokuba ziintsomi zabantu bakudala”
  23,84,"Yithi: (Muhammad), “Ngokabani na umhlaba noko kuphakathi kuwo, ukuba nini abaziyo"
  23,85,"Baza kuthi bona: “Ngoka-Allâh.” Yithi wena: “Ingaba ke ngoku aniyi kukhumbula?”"
  23,86,"Yithi: “Ngubani iNkosi yamazulu asixhenxe noyiNkosi yeTrone eNkulu?”"
  23,87,"Baza kuthi bona: “Zezika-Allâh.” Yithi wena: “Ingaba ke nina anizi kuMoyika uAllâh"
  23,88,"Yithi: “Lukwesikabani iSandla ulongamelo lwezinto zonke inguYe nje Okhuselayo lo gama kungekho bani unokukhuselwa ngokuchasene naYe xa ngaba phofu niyazi?”"
  23,89,"Baza kuthi bona: “Lukwesika-Allâh.” Yithi: “Ke ngoku nikhohliseke njani nina?”"
  23,90,"Ukusuka apho Thina Sibazele nenyaniso, yaye inene bona ngamaxoki"
  23,91,"UAllâh Akazelanga nyana, kungazanga kwabakho omnye uthixo okunye naYe Yena. (ukuba bekukho omnye uthixo kunye naYe) uthixo ngamnye ebeza kuthabatha okudalwe nguye, ukanti abanye kubo bebeza kufuna ukongamela abanye. Uzuko malube kuYe Yena Uphakamile koko bakubalela (kuYe)"
  23,92,"(Yena) nguMazi wokungabonwayo nokubonwayo, ngoko ke Yena Uphakamele phezulu koko bakwayamanisa (naYe)"